issue.body:
Please add a getter to ClassInfo to determine if the class is package/default visible.

Maybe something like
```java
    /**
     * Checks if the class has default aka package visiblity.
     * 
     * @return true if this class is only visible within it's package
     */
    public boolean isPackageVisible() {
        return !isPublic() && !isPrivate() && !isProtected();
        // or
        return modifiers & (Modifier.PUBLIC | Modifier.PRIVATE | Modifier.PROTECTED)) == 0;
    }
```

